f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:38:29.000Z","msg":"窮就咪柒養啦<br />\n<br />\n你老豆窮人屌西唔帶套生你出來受苦你都嬲佢啦<br />\n<br />\n你想唔想隻貓嬲你？<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"喂傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24913bfc7d4ee80b79dea2d05585160885878d6e","tid":1947783,"uid":248293,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:41:31.000Z","msg":"一蚊都唔洗<br />\n佢肚餓就掉佢係逸東邨養一個月ok"},{"pid":"e4bf4765a8e649c48c96dff773d6195e69f1a666","tid":1947783,"uid":272202,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"認真答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重要嘅嘢講咗先 請領養代替購買<br />\n唔係名種貓其實都可以好乖好嗲好健康<br />\n最重要係隻貓同你夾唔夾 佢唔中意你嘅話同冇養冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以去花園望下睇下有冇合眼緣嘅貓<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://instagram.com/little.bean.ding?igshid=1sar4mvavp4zx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Flittle.bean.ding%3Figshid%3D1sar4mvavp4zx&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=47323937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/little.bean.ding?igshid=1sar4mvavp4zx</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓嘅洗費可以睇好味小姐呢條片了解下<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/7ENaBNc0ehg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7ENaBNc0ehg&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=683c98a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7ENaBNc0ehg</a></blockquote><br />\n佢係台灣人 講嘅係台幣 物價同香港有差別 你可以自己google下啲嘢香港買要幾多錢<br />\n好味小姐啲片都好啱新手貓奴睇 呢幾條片我認為可以幫你了解下點樣養貓<br />\n<blockquote>貓食:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/g14_W-H3c20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fg14_W-H3c20&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=681f58fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/g14_W-H3c20</a><br />\n貓砂:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_cu13RH88Jw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_cu13RH88Jw&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=c8f94747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_cu13RH88Jw</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓糧有好多種 可以參考下巴絲整理嘅呢個post<br />\n糧嘅質素同價錢係成正比 想貓健康嘅話要揀好啲 當然要睇番隻糧同隻貓本身夾唔夾 最好佢本來食邊隻就餵番邊隻 但你覺得可以換再好啲嘅都可以慢慢試下轉糧 睇佢o唔ok<br />\n超市紫色包裝W字頭嗰類就唔洗諗啦<br />\n<blockquote>貓糧資料庫（5）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1060673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1060673</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我主子唔係英短 但有朋友係養英短 嗰陣陪佢去買 大約6k~10k 都冇話有乜特別需要<br />\n只係會成日想買嘢俾佢食買嘢俾佢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4459b531245d40b84c3fd1d71c8c41016f75908","tid":1947783,"uid":299102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:06:11.000Z","msg":"一開始養貓淨係買日常生活既野都用咗三四千 睇醫生用咗一千左右"},{"pid":"7395797204547d1ddb67818425a859f4cf8bdda5","tid":1947783,"uid":82214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4bf4765a8e649c48c96dff773d6195e69f1a666","tid":1947783,"uid":272202,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"認真答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重要嘅嘢講咗先 請領養代替購買<br />\n唔係名種貓其實都可以好乖好嗲好健康<br />\n最重要係隻貓同你夾唔夾 佢唔中意你嘅話同冇養冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以去花園望下睇下有冇合眼緣嘅貓<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://instagram.com/little.bean.ding?igshid=1sar4mvavp4zx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Flittle.bean.ding%3Figshid%3D1sar4mvavp4zx&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=47323937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/little.bean.ding?igshid=1sar4mvavp4zx</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓嘅洗費可以睇好味小姐呢條片了解下<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/7ENaBNc0ehg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7ENaBNc0ehg&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=683c98a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7ENaBNc0ehg</a></blockquote><br />\n佢係台灣人 講嘅係台幣 物價同香港有差別 你可以自己google下啲嘢香港買要幾多錢<br />\n好味小姐啲片都好啱新手貓奴睇 呢幾條片我認為可以幫你了解下點樣養貓<br />\n<blockquote>貓食:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/g14_W-H3c20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fg14_W-H3c20&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=681f58fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/g14_W-H3c20</a><br />\n貓砂:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_cu13RH88Jw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_cu13RH88Jw&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=c8f94747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_cu13RH88Jw</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓糧有好多種 可以參考下巴絲整理嘅呢個post<br />\n糧嘅質素同價錢係成正比 想貓健康嘅話要揀好啲 當然要睇番隻糧同隻貓本身夾唔夾 最好佢本來食邊隻就餵番邊隻 但你覺得可以換再好啲嘅都可以慢慢試下轉糧 睇佢o唔ok<br />\n超市紫色包裝W字頭嗰類就唔洗諗啦<br />\n<blockquote>貓糧資料庫（5）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1060673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1060673</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我主子唔係英短 但有朋友係養英短 嗰陣陪佢去買 大約6k~10k 都冇話有乜特別需要<br />\n只係會成日想買嘢俾佢食買嘢俾佢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:13:27.000Z","msg":"一直都有睇開養貓片 不過係去到真係想買之前想睇下洗費大約幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335aced50d887024b8b3d7d1c9e3d60f232e22c0","tid":1947783,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61913660fc220ccd95c95648c1ee089fa73e5c3b","tid":1947783,"uid":40470,"like":7,"dislike":28,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"fb3b0dafec524a55e39e1ec9dca98d691bae2559","tid":1947783,"uid":82214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"想知買貓大概幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋一個月大約要洗幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:38:29.000Z","msg":"窮就咪柒養啦<br />\n<br />\n你老豆窮人屌西唔帶套生你出來受苦你都嬲佢啦<br />\n<br />\n你想唔想隻貓嬲你？<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"同意 樓主正窮閪"},{"pid":"9693baab9e08a32dd2c4b50dd13fd0dc0a9f5ea8","tid":1947783,"uid":3539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"就算平時養貓平<br />\n一睇醫生咪又係要洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053dfb19346deb6e590904bd4f5cb57324796c75","tid":1947783,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:31:52.000Z","msg":"最貴係睇醫生<br />\n一個唔好彩大病就要你幾皮<br />\n健健康康就幾百一個月"},{"pid":"a097204bb3892ff9f3b2767f6893bd7cc82e842f","tid":1947783,"uid":121058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"平均一個月拉均計~1000<br />\n化毛膏 營養膚 200/mo<br />\n貓砂 100/mo<br />\n貓鑵 250/mo <br />\n貓糧 150/mo<br />\n貓玩具 100/mo<br />\n貓零食 100/mo<br />\n<br />\n我隻貓養左5年 無大病 每年打針感冒牙科<br />\n平均一年4000蚊左右"},{"pid":"c1f7e8b415694d5e6ddfa814d2c956085f7343d2","tid":1947783,"uid":8827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"053dfb19346deb6e590904bd4f5cb57324796c75","tid":1947783,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:31:52.000Z","msg":"最貴係睇醫生<br />\n一個唔好彩大病就要你幾皮<br />\n健健康康就幾百一個月"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:32:42.000Z","msg":"啱 正常幾百 睇醫生無上限"},{"pid":"303f5b20b14f5fb294b32229c6c4d424a55e5202","tid":1947783,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"十萬公里要番廠大整"},{"pid":"cbaa4eba24eaab23263f0f670b855f08518e6fb6","tid":1947783,"uid":39564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T20:07:48.000Z","msg":"貓砂100 蚊<br />\n貓糧300蚊 <br />\n零食罐罐300蚊<br />\n玩具10蚊<br />\n<br />\n打針絕育睇醫生另計<br />\n初初 買左好多野比佢玩佢都唔會玩 <br />\n搞到益曬我隻狗"},{"pid":"7276ea4bb7821936d62d739e960d3acc7d4111a6","tid":1947783,"uid":120564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:25:19.000Z","msg":"一開始買生活用品洗左4,5千<br />\n日常最貴係買罐<br />\n我主子多數食罐罐同凍乾<br />\n乾糧長放不過佢好少食<br />\n一個月既罐罐差唔多500咁上下<br />\n凍乾又會再貴啲<br />\n<br />\n不過罐都有平有貴 睇你買咩比佢食<br />\n食乾糧就平好多 <br />\n不過好似對主子健康冇咁好"},{"pid":"69adb4a101e0f3b71780dee5df6b1beeb7dbb1a0","tid":1947783,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:26:46.000Z","msg":"賤養1000蚊<br />\n<br />\n貴養3000蚊"},{"pid":"f7f0f82e3735e1410e183978829ce3be3f02c0fb","tid":1947783,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:31:58.000Z","msg":"唔病既話冇乜野，濕糧10幾蚊一罐，乾糧一大包好平有排食，好少少既話一個月400 到600 啦。<br />\n<br />\n但佢一病你就頭痕，我個隻有日唔知做乜嘔左成日，睇一睇急症打針照野抽血留醫住院，埋單差唔多1萬。<br />\n<br />\n另一隻偶然咳左得幾勁，帶佢睇醫生之後好驚抽筋，又抽血照x光留左一晚醫房，埋單又一萬。<br />\n<br />\n純種貓通常多病痛d，淨係食乾糧唔多飲水易有尿道炎，記得比濕糧同多d飲水啦。"},{"pid":"880231d48f03ca76b60fc3ced0a45c228307e542","tid":1947783,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T14:43:15.000Z","msg":"Around $1700-2700每個月<br />\n計埋寵物保險"}]}